<section class="why-choose-us section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Why Choose Edwards & Smith?</h2>
      <p>We understand the challenges buyers face. Here's how we help.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <!-- Interstate Buyers -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Don't Know the Market?</h3>
        <p class="benefit-question">Moving to Brisbane or Gold Coast from interstate?</p>
        <p class="benefit-answer">We're your local experts with deep knowledge of every suburb, school zone, and hidden gem. Our relationships with local agents give you insider access before properties hit the market.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Market expertise across all Queensland regions</li>
          <li>School catchment zone specialists</li>
          <li>Deep agent relationships for off-market access</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Time-Poor Professionals -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>No Time to Search?</h3>
        <p class="benefit-question">Busy with work, family, or living interstate?</p>
        <p class="benefit-answer">We do all the heavy lifting. From initial search to final inspection, we handle everything while you focus on what matters. We search 40+ properties weekly so you don't have to.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Save 50+ hours of searching and inspecting</li>
          <li>We attend inspections on your behalf</li>
          <li>Handle all paperwork and due diligence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Frustrated Buyers -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Keep Missing Out?</h3>
        <p class="benefit-question">Tired of losing properties to other buyers?</p>
        <p class="benefit-answer">We move fast and negotiate with authority. Real estate agents know our clients are serious buyers with finance ready. You get preference because agents trust there's no risk of the deal falling through.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Buyers agents given preference by sellers</li>
          <li>Average purchase time: 4 weeks</li>
          <li>Finance pre-approval ensures deal certainty</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Off-Market Access -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Access to Off-Market Properties</h3>
        <p class="benefit-question">Want properties before they hit the market?</p>
        <p class="benefit-answer">Our deep relationships with selling agents across Queensland give you exclusive access to properties before the public knows they exist. Less competition means better prices and faster deals.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>Exclusive off-market property database</li>
          <li>First access before public listings</li>
          <li>Less competition = better negotiating power</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-center">
      <a href="/consultation" class="button-primary">See How We Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-choose-us {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--body-large);
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .benefit-question {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .benefit-answer {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .benefit-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .benefit-list li {
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .benefit-list li::before {
    content: 'âœ“';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .cta-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
